snippet.title: TT Isle of Man - Ride on the Edge 3 | Section 5 of the Snaefell Mountain Course
snippet.description:
At the NACON Connect Winter, we have exclusively revealed the first minute of our new gameplay sequence. 

This time we control Dean Harrison on his 2022 Kawazaki ZX-10RR in section 5 of the Snaefell Mountain circuit. 

What are your impressions on this new section?
